OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIncreasingly
OL,6,Fcloudy this evening with a chance of a
OL,7,Ffew spots of light rain. The rest of
OL,8,Fthe night will be mainly dry with
OL,9,Fclear spells and freshening winds.
OL,10,FBecoming cloudy towards the north
OL,11,Fcoast by morning with patchy rain.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FCloudy with patchy light
OL,14,Frain spreading southeast through the
OL,15,Fmorning. Then turning drier and
OL,16,Fbrighter for a time into the
OL,17,Fafternoon. Cloudy and patchy rain
OL,18,Fspread west in the evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
