OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FBright
OL,6,Fspells and scattered showers on
OL,7,FSunday. Fairly unsettled and
OL,8,Fchangeable Monday and Tuesday with the
OL,9,Frisk of further showers or spells of
OL,10,Frain.
